title: World Series, Cowboys, Anthony Davis, and Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: World Series, Cowboys, Anthony Davis, and Baker Mayfield
description:
Colin explains how the Nationals did the right thing with Stephen Strasburg, the Cowboys going cheap at the trade deadline, what worries him about Anthony Davis, and his thoughts on Baker Mayfield's latest drama. Guests include Nick Wright, Albert Breer, Joel Klatt, Sam Monson, John Smoltz.
